  "serviceNotes": {
    "engine oil": "PHEV models still require petrol engine maintenance on Mercedes EU schedules (typically 15,000 km or 12 months for oil when the combustion engine runs enough to reach distance limits\u2014ASSYST adjusts for hybrid use).",
